    "description": "《英灵战士》是一款养成塔防游戏，你需要获取不断的金币来升级你的英灵战士及装备。每位英灵战士擅长的武器、天赋、被动技能都不同。<br><br>您可以随意进行武器搭配。谁说弓只能射出箭？你可以把你多余的其他武器当作弓箭射出去！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.poster.avif?t=1681371367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.webm?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.mp4?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>丢出去武器的不同可能会对怪物造成不同的负面状态，例如过敏等。<br>另外，可千万不能让英灵战士拿到那个武器熟练度为负的武器，否则会大大增加你的难度！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.poster.avif?t=1681371367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.webm?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.mp4?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏内容：<br>·6种职业：弓箭手、法师、枪兵、剑士、投掷手、纯纯的废物（没有伤害武器）<br>·40+英灵战士。<br>·40+被动技能<br>·80+件装备和70+件武器<br>·150+怪物<br>·7种Debuff：流血、眩晕、燃烧、冰冻、减速、中毒、过敏。<br>·150个关卡+1个最终战。<br><br>祝你好运！",
